org.neo4j.remote
Class RemoteResponse<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.neo4j.remote.RemoteResponse<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the requested data
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public abstract class RemoteResponse<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable

Represents a response to request sent to a RemoteConnection. The RemoteResponse contains at least the data that was requested but may also contain additional data. For example data that the client have requested before that have been updated on the server, or data that is very likely that the client will need soon given the request it has made.
